_sText:
My first gungame map.  Meant to be the first public test release, so download it and put it on your server then tell me what people think about it!

Two spawn areas, holding up to a maximum of 24 persons on each team (reccomend about 12 each team).  This map is a fun one to play, and it's not huge and overly spacious.  

One thing... DONT FALL OFF!  Lol.  Yeah It's about a 300-ft drop to the bottom.

My xfire is in my profile here or in the readme.txt inside the folder.

Make sure to give me suggestions on what to add for v2b!
